    dc:description "FIGURE 2. Holotype of Pristimantis yantzaza sp. nov. in life, FHGO 9962, adult female, SVL 24.4 mm: A) dorsal view, and B) ventral view." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/1065754/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.1065756>
    dc:description "FIGURE 3. Holotype of Pristimantis yantzaza sp. nov. (FHGO 9962, adult female, SVL 24.4 mm) in preservative: A) dorsal view, B) ventral view, C) head, dorsal view, and D) head, lateral view." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/1065756/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.1065762>
    dc:description "FIGURE 4. Hand and feet of the holotype of Pristimantis yantzaza sp. nov. in preservative FHGO 58044, adult female: A) palmar view of hand, B) plantar view of foot." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/1065762/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.1065764>
    dc:description "FIGURE 5. Live specimens of Pristimantis yantzaza sp. nov. showing variation in dorsal and ventral coloration. From left to right, first and second rows: FHGO 9965, FHGO 9963, QCAZ 47544, QCAZ 47545 (females), third and fourth rows: QCAZ 65095, QCAZ 65098, QCAZ 65099, QCAZ 65112 (males).All specimens are shown in the same scale." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/1065764/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.1065766>
    dc:description "FIGURE6. Oscillogram and spectrogram of the advertisement call of Pristimantis yantzaza sp. nov. (unvoucheredspecimen)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/1065766/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.1065768>
    dc:description "FIGURE 7. Distribution of Pristimantis yantzaza sp. nov. (triangles) in eastern Ecuador.The blue pentagon indicates the type locality." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/1065768/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.1065770>
    dc:description "FIGURE 8. A) Panoramic view of the habitat of Pristimantis yantzaza sp. nov., Cordillera del Condor; near Los Encuentros, Zamora Chinchipe; B) habitat at the type locality; C) an adult female perching on leaves at Palanda; and D) an adult female camouflaged on moss at Tundayme." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/1065770/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

